snippet.title: Johnny Depp & Amber Heard: We Chat About Johnny's Times Interview and Other Updates
snippet.description:
Amber Heard / Johnny Depp / The Times Interview / 

We discuss the latest in Amber Heard and Johnny Depp controversy, including Johnny Depp's latest interview with the big London newspaper The Times. 

Subscribe to me channel for parts 2 and 3 of this conversation.

And this is Colonel Kurtz's channel if you're interested in hearing more from her: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAxriNBFZQPTsj9vBOSnhkA
